						<summary>

						<p>On a second slab set up in a grove called the Polimēratōpu.</p>						

						<p>This records the death of Munichōre of, Vempaḷḷi son of Gaṇḍachabuli, in a fight. The epigraph is engraved in archaic characters of the 7th century A.D. </p>						

